
Package: TreeTwoWay
Type: Package
Title: Likelihood Ratio and MinMin/MinMax Tests for Two-Way ANOVA Under Tree Order Restriction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Susmita", "Chawlia",
           email = "susmitachawlia16@kgpian.iitkgp.ac.in",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides hypothesis testing procedures for two-way ANOVA
    under tree-order restrictions. The package implements the
    Likelihood Ratio Test (TreeLRT), the MinMin test (TreeMinMin),
    and the MinMax test (TreeMinMax). Critical values are obtained
    using a parametric bootstrap under heteroscedasticity and
    unequal sample sizes.
